{"_id":"01b1941a-1a64-4b6d-934a-91703f09720e","type":"ability","name":"Martial Arts","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/athletics.svg","system":{"skill":"Athletics","name":"Martial Arts","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You must have the Boxer ability to select this. Your unarmed attacks can now also be made as Fast actions that deal Light damage or Slow actions that deal Heavy damage.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Physical","costtype":"","skill_id":"athletics"}}
{"_id":"2e636c6c-7fad-45e4-b96e-1615f3deec9c","type":"ability","name":"Push Through","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/athletics.svg","system":{"skill":"Athletics","name":"Push Through","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"At any time during your turn, you can spend 1 Vigour to ignore the effects of the Dazed, Weakened, Slowed, Burning, Charged, and Corroding conditions until the end of your next turn. If you spend 2 Vigour instead, you also ignore all penalties from stat burn.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Physical","costtype":"vigour","skill_id":"athletics"}}
{"_id":"69dd2aad-b62e-4d89-b807-96a8b62becda","type":"ability","name":"Distance Runner","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/athletics.svg","system":{"skill":"Athletics","name":"Distance Runner","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"1 Hour","cost":"1","description":"For the next hour, you do not tire from moving long distances carrying normal amounts of gear. You gain a boon on all checks made to move quickly over long distances. If the GM determines that your travel would cause you to burn Strength, you may use this ability to negate that burn.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Physical","costtype":"vigour","skill_id":"athletics"}}
{"_id":"81c0fc8e-9786-46ac-b2f6-883982ac18ca","type":"ability","name":"Feats of Strength","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/athletics.svg","system":{"skill":"Athletics","name":"Feats of Strength","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"1 Minute","cost":"3","description":"You can perform incredible feats of strength. When you use this ability, your physical prowess is improved beyond the natural for up to a minute. You gain a boon to Athletics checks, and can do things impossible to normal people, such as breaking through stone walls with your bare fists, throwing person-sized objects dozens of meters, or lifting an autocart over your head. Once during the course of this time, you gain an Epic Boon on a strength-based check.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Physical","costtype":"vigour","skill_id":"athletics"}}
{"_id":"9d1b14f7-14de-4f7c-832f-0ee2b25c3ffa","type":"ability","name":"Sprinter","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/athletics.svg","system":{"skill":"Athletics","name":"Sprinter","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"1 Minute","cost":"1","description":"For the next minute, you gain a Boon on all checks to move quickly, including in combat.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Physical","costtype":"vigour","skill_id":"athletics"}}
