{"_id":"da46e9ed-be5e-479b-b61c-f5f710987719","type":"skill","name":"Athletics","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/athletics.svg","system":{"skill_id":"athletics","domain":"Physical","rank":1,"stat":"strength","description":"The Athletics skill is used in climbing, swimming, running, and jumping. Moving heavy objects, breaking down doors, and tossing your dwarven companion into a group of enemies all use your athletics skill. It often overlaps with Acrobatics; Athletics is used when strength and endurance matter more."}}
{"_id":"e8a372a2-cf4f-4d31-99e1-6c5738eece86","type":"ability","name":"Boxer","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/athletics.svg","system":{"skill":"Athletics","name":"Boxer","rank":"1","type":"weapon","action":"medium","defense":"agility","target":"Single","range":"Adjacent","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You use the Athletics skill to make unarmed attacks. Your basic unarmed attacks can be made as Medium actions that deal Standard damage. These attacks can be made even when your hands are occupied by using your feet, head, or whole body.","roll_type":"","domain":"Physical","costtype":"","skill_id":"athletics"}}
